<head>CHAPTER XVII</head>



<div class="opener">



<div type="textpart" subtype="argument">


<list><item>Foundation of Constantinople</item> <item>Political System of Constantine, and his Successors</item> <item>Military Discipline</item> <item>The Palace</item> <item>The Finances</item></list>



