<note xml:id="ch20n80"><p id="ch20n80pa1">Philostorgius, l. iii. c. 4, 5, 6, with Godefroy's learned observations. The historical narrative is soon lost in an inquiry concerning the seat of paradise, strange monsters, &amp;c.</p></note>

